"title": "7209: congregation",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7209: congregation",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A group of people gathered or called together for a purpose. In Scripture a congregation refers particularly to the Israelites gathered for worship; it is also used of Christians in the NT.</p>\n<h2>The congregation of the Israelites</h2>\n<h3>For the giving of the Ten Commandments</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:17\">EXO 19:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:22\">DEU 5:22</a></p>\n<h3>For hearing God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:1-Neh8:9\">NEH 8:1–8:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:1\">DEU 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:18\">NEH 8:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:1-Neh9:3\">NEH 9:1–9:3</a></p>\n<h3>For praising God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:22\">PSA 22:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:9-Ps40:10\">PSA 40:9–40:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:26\">PSA 68:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:12\">HEB 2:12</a></p>\n<h3>To make a sin offering for the sin of the community</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev4:13-Lev4:14\">LEV 4:13–4:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:24\">NUM 15:24</a></p>\n<h3>For the ordination of priests and Levites</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:3-Lev8:4\">LEV 8:3–8:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:9\">NUM 8:9</a></p>\n<h3>For census, retribution and major events</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:14\">LEV 24:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num1:18\">NUM 1:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh18:1\">JOS 18:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:1\">JDG 20:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:17\">1SA 10:17</a></p>\n<h3>Exclusion from the assembly</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:1-Deut23:8\">DEU 23:1–23:8</a></p>\n<h2>In the NT</h2>\n<h3>Jewish congregations in the synagogue</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:20\">LUK 4:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:5\">ACT 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:14-Acts13:15\">ACT 13:14–13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:1\">ACT 14:1</a></p>\n<h3>Christian congregations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:46-Acts2:47\">ACT 2:46–2:47</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:12\">ACT 5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:26\">ACT 11:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:7\">ACT 20:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:33-1Cor14:34\">1CO 14:33–14:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:2\">JAS 2:2</a></p>",
